<li>1750â1758: <a href="/w/index.php?title=Ernst_Matthaeus_Kummer&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Ernst Matthaeus Kummer (page does not exist)">Ernst Matthaeus Kummer</a></li>
<li>1758â1770: W.C. Steinhaeuser</li>
<li>1770â1775: Weiss</li>
