<li>1815â1830: <a href="/w/index.php?title=Christoph_Friedrich_Krenkel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Christoph Friedrich Krenkel (page does not exist)">Christoph Friedrich Krenkel</a></li>
