<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Other_sites_of_interest">Other sites of interest</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Pforzheim&amp;action=edit&amp;section=34" title="Edit section: Other sites of interest">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
