<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Famous_citizens_born_in_Pforzheim">Famous citizens born in Pforzheim</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Pforzheim&amp;action=edit&amp;section=38" title="Edit section: Famous citizens born in Pforzheim">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
