<li><span class="citation wikicite" id="endnote_hist8"><b><a href="#ref_hist8">^</a></b></span> <a href="#References">References</a> Hans-Peter Becht: Pforzheim in der fruehen Neuzeit, chapter "Melanchthons Pforzheimer Schulzeit", pp.&#160;9â50.</li>
